<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Akses Ditolak - Arsip Surat Digital Enterprise">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#1a56db">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
    <title>403 - Akses Ditolak | Arsip Surat Digital Enterprise</title>
    
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1a56db;
            --primary-dark: #1e40af;
            --secondary: #64748b;
            --warning: #f59e0b;
            --dark: #1f2937;
            --light: #f9fafb;
            --lighter: #ffffff;
            --border: #e5e7eb;
            --font-sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            --shadow-lg: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            --radius-lg: 16px;
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body {
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffbeb 0%, #fef3c7 50%, #fef2f2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .error-container {
            background: var(--lighter);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 100px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--warning);
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .error-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .info-card {
            background: #fffbeb;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .info-card h3 {
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .info-card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }
        
        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
            font-family: var(--font-sans);
        }
        
        .btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: white; border-color: var(--primary); }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); border-color: var(--primary-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .btn-outline { background: transparent; color: var(--primary); border-color: var(--primary); }
        .btn-outline:hover { background: var(--primary); color: white; transform: translateY(-2px); }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .error-container { padding: 40px 20px; }
            .error-code { font-size: 70px; }
            .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">🔒</div>
        <div class="error-code">403</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">Akses Ditolak</h1>
        <p class="error-message">
            Anda tidak memiliki izin untuk mengakses halaman ini. 
            Silakan hubungi administrator jika Anda merasa seharusnya memiliki akses.
        </p>
        
        <div class="info-card">
            <h3>📋 Kemungkinan Penyebab:</h3>
            <p>• Anda belum login ke sistem</p>
            <p>• Role/level akses Anda tidak mencukupi</p>
            <p>• Sesi login Anda telah berakhir</p>
            <p>• Halaman ini khusus untuk role tertentu</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="btn-group">
            <a href="../../login" class="btn btn-primary">🔐 Login</a>
            <a href="../../" class="btn btn-outline">🏠 Ke Beranda</a>
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-outline">← Kembali</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
